1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with detecting and tracking objects in imagery using Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs). 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses unsupervised methods and machine learning techniques to improve object detection. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses CNNs to reject false alarms and predict the positions of multiple moving objects. 
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper discusses multi-target tracking, which is a common problem in robotics. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with processing and analyzing motion imagery.
